{"tid":1428232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[真正專家]湯博士: 係叫做激光指示筆 (laser pointer)，唔係叫雷射槍，亦都唔係叫觀星筆","createTime":"2019-08-07T09:11:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T10:44:48.000Z","uid":240362,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"36045b87868b0e20aeb8c62f0b2a35d709edd7db","tid":1428232,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67729115_2070852939884984_6182885875366494208_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQl7SIjHN-r5YqDIbNjHEmokT1B-a0vrFABNguY3gPlYF8vli2zhCFpYFUVMd61lq9c&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=291b2049821a3187f840f8a3d346fba5&amp;oe=5DDC5EE3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67729115_2070852939884984_6182885875366494208_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQl7SIjHN-r5YqDIbNjHEmokT1B-a0vrFABNguY3gPlYF8vli2zhCFpYFUVMd61lq9c%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D291b2049821a3187f840f8a3d346fba5%26oe%3D5DDC5EE3&h=ca62712f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n*實在太忙，未得閒回應*<br />\n<br />\n作為一個從事物理和天文教育的人，擁有半打激光指示筆，係好合理嘅。<br />\n<br />\n係叫做激光指示筆 (laser pointer)，唔係叫雷射槍，亦都唔係叫觀星筆！😈<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 剛剛在物理教育期刊發表了一篇文章，示範怎樣用藍光 laser (405 nm)在湯力水 (tonic water) 中產生螢光，讓學生可以清楚看見光的路徑，示範幾何光學的現象 (照片為全內反射的示範)，各位老師可以參考。我擁有半打 pointer, 就係為了產生多束光線。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldscientific.com/doi/10.1142/S2661339519500069?fbclid=IwAR3BJT1KO96qHuHuQvGNRmw_BOLZ12IP61R_Qdnd7yczTKYTNZJUHYncDbc&amp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldscientific.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1142%2FS2661339519500069%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3BJT1KO96qHuHuQvGNRmw_BOLZ12IP61R_Qdnd7yczTKYTNZJUHYncDbc%26&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ4uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=3e14d703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldscientific.com/doi/10.1142/S2661339519500069?fbclid=IwAR3BJT1KO96qHuHuQvGNRmw_BOLZ12IP61R_Qdnd7yczTKYTNZJUHYncDbc&amp;</a>"},{"pid":"946ad561d3854e9a806bf8ce3612fc51adcd1eeb","tid":1428232,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:12:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0363f14e69b4805a5b81d715c2c7ee2109358dc5","tid":1428232,"uid":67574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:13:29.000Z","msg":"堆"},{"pid":"f5b99dfe47d99792d94c4709954defb6843113f3","tid":1428232,"uid":89229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:14:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4a247fe3bd665ff9210294ed69523b7bfa7f98b","tid":1428232,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:17:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/drtongsharing/photos/a.1481208422182775/2070852936551651/?type=3&amp;permPage=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdrtongsharing%2Fphotos%2Fa.1481208422182775%2F2070852936551651%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26permPage%3D1&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ4uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=d67cd536\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/drtongsharing/photos/a.1481208422182775/2070852936551651/?type=3&amp;permPage=1</a>"},{"pid":"c6b08bafe3d19b93e60d4536fa077968f0913b14","tid":1428232,"uid":199487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:44:48.000Z","msg":"push"}]}